file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Unix Counter (Server)
  version: ${project.version}
  license:
    name: Apache License Version 2.0
    url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/
paths: { }
components:
  schemas:
    RegisteredReportData:
      description: POJO that represents the information for counting a host.
      required:
        - system_id
        - kernel_name
        - kernel_version
        - distribution_name
        - distribution_version
        - timezone
      type: object
      properties:
        system_id:
          type: string
        kernel_name:
          type: string
        kernel_version:
          type: string
        distribution_name:
          type: string
        distribution_version:
          type: string
        timezone:
          type: string
    AnonymousReportData:
      description: POJO that represents the information for counting a host.
      required:
        - kernel_name
        - kernel_version
        - distribution_name
        - distribution_version
        - timezone
        - hardware_id
      type: object
      properties:
        kernel_name:
          type: string
        kernel_version:
          type: string
        distribution_name:
          type: string
        distribution_version:
          type: string
        timezone:
          type: string
        hardware_id:
          type: string
